==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Flaring
<hw>Flar"ing</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>That
flares; flaming or blazing unsteadily; shining out with a dazzling
light.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>His [the sun's] <qex>flaring</qex> beams.</q>
<rj><qau>Milton.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Opening or spreading outwards.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Flaringly</ent>⟦br⟧
